me.hyperperform.rest

Class ReportingRest

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.hyperperform.rest.ReportingRest

  • @Path(value="/report")
public class ReportingRest
extends Object
    REST wraps the IReport interface. A concrete realization is injected into the object. The services provided by the IReport interface are then made available through REST endpoints.
    Since:
    : 2016/08/10
    Version:
